Pressure</h3>\n<table width=\"100%\" class=\"tborder\">\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Names</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">WilePressure <i><font size=\"-2\">",
    "</font></i></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Country</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">[Unknown]</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Motivation</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?m=Information%20theft%20and%20espionage\" title=\"Search for all threat groups with motivation Information theft and espionage\" class=\"inlink\">Information theft and espionage</a></td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">First seen</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">2019</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Description</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">",
    "In August 2019, Kaspersky discovered a malicious campaign distributing a fully fledged C++ Trojan that we call Milum. All the victims we registered were organizations from the Middle East. At least some of them are related to industrial sector. Our Kaspersky Threat Attribution Engine",
    "doesn’t show any code similarities with known campaigns. Nor have we seen any target intersections. In fact, we found just three almost unique samples, all in one country. So we consider the attacks to be targeted and have currently named this operation WildPressure.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Observed</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">Sectors: <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Industrial\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Industrial\" class=\"inlink\">Industrial</a>, <a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?s=Oil%20and%20gas\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that target Oil and gas\" class=\"inlink\">Oil and gas</a>.<br />Countries: Middle East.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Tools used</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\"><a href=\"/cgi-bin/listgroups.cgi?t=Milum\" title=\"Search for all threat groups that use Milum\" class=\"inlink\">Milum</a>.</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" rowspan=\"1\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Operations performed</td><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\">Spring 2021</td><td valign=\"top\" width=\"100%\">WildPressure targets the macOS platform<br />&lt;<a href=\"https://securelist.com/wildpressure-targets-macos/103072/\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://securelist.com/wildpressure-targets-macos/103072/</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n<tr><td nowrap valign=\"top\" width=\"0%\" class=\"tshaded\">Information</td><td valign=\"top\" colspan=\"2\" width=\"100%\">&lt;<a href=\"https://securelist.com/wildpressure-targets-industrial-in-the-middle-east/96360/\" title=\"Follow external link\" class=\"exlink\" target=\"_blank\">https://securelist.com/wildpressure-targets-industrial-in-the-middle-east/96360/</a>&gt;</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p>Last change to this card: 09 August 2021</p>\n<p>Download this actor card in <a href=\"/cgi-bin/getcard.cgi?g=WildPressure&o=p\" title=\"